title: Fashion label Sentaler basks in 'Meghan effect'
text:
Fashion label Sentaler basks in 'Meghan effect' 1:28am GMT - 01:29 
Canadian luxury label Sentaler hosts a private showcase at London Fashion Week, aiming to capitalize on its recent association with Meghan Markle, the actress fiancée of Britain's Prince Harry. Rough Cut - no reporter narration ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
